        "results": "The univariate analysis confirmed that low BAG1 expression (p=0.0041) was linked to poor overall survival (OS) and disease-specific survival (DSS), while high BAG2 expression (p=0.0312) was associated with adverse OS and DSS in patients with dedifferentiated liposarcoma (DDLPS). The multivariate analysis indicated that reduced BAG1 expression (p=0.043, HR=0.231, 95% CI [0.056\u20130.955]) remained a significant independent prognostic factor.",
        "results original text": "In detail, DDLPS patients with low BAG1 expression were significantly associated with poor OS (p=0.0041) and DSS (p=0.0111), while high BAG2 expression predicted worse OS and DSS (p=0.0312)."
